{"tid":1662153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［林鄭睇到請入］比起你，陳同佳更加識點做一個人","createTime":"2019-10-18T14:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T15:50:56.000Z","uid":17024,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f21b27fc0f5261a9b3c81c8f7d850c247d2c87","tid":1662153,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:48:16.000Z","msg":"無可否認<br />\n如果唔係佢台灣殺人<br />\n成件事係唔會發生<br />\n但佢比起你<br />\n多咗一樣野<br />\n而呢樣野係你呢世都唔會有<br />\n就係反省嘅心<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳係咩原因令佢諗通咗要去台灣自首都好<br />\n係因為殺人內疚、因為香港搞成咁而內疚<br />\n最後佢都肯承擔佢應該要承擔嘅後果<br />\n<br />\n反觀林鄭你自己，因為你嘅硬頸、你嘅固執、你嘅自私、想邀功嘅心<br />\n令香港去到番唔到轉頭嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n老實講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你衰過一個殺人犯</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你唔止唔配做香港特首，你連做香港人嘅資格都冇。因我係你出賣香港人、係你令到香港變成咁</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc395a3b3be64a4da5a6c224b9aa9ad4877d0f00","tid":1662153,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:48:55.000Z","msg":"只抒己見"},{"pid":"5bec093da904b5fada8870fc150f9594fe5ac0e4","tid":1662153,"uid":293783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"應晒，垃圾林奠"},{"pid":"12ad3178704a480e296670450c816b38b201086a","tid":1662153,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"*借位post*<br />\n<br />\n記得send文宣俾朋友拉人去！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1020香港人全民召集<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/18/222059_10967b4045cae79ea56bc8beb1bdfbfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F18%2F222059_10967b4045cae79ea56bc8beb1bdfbfc.png&h=564f4b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理為盾，勇武為矛，和勇一家互相合作我地先會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買幾多coupon、捐幾多物資，都比唔上用人數證明俾港共睇香港人冇驚過，亦證明俾勇武睇 我地係核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">要記住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">多你一個好撚多<br />\n我地一定會贏</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1020九龍見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"121d627286778abf28bd865e6f2e5ae6971d059b","tid":1662153,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"真正既盤係中共想用逃犯條例 反擊孟晚丹單野咋<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳只係藉口"},{"pid":"9b1ea0c3adfa818ecad16e72723d34b64e23f08f","tid":1662153,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"383fb81ab985e14fa74176b519880ee61ec8c987","tid":1662153,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}